{{#is_alert}}

## What's happening?
The ClickHouse background merge pool on {{host.name}} has a high number of active merge tasks. This may indicate write pressure exceeding the merge throughput, or merges being blocked by long-running operations.

## How to investigate
Check `system.merges` for currently running merges. Consider reducing insert frequency, increasing `background_pool_size`, or investigating mutations blocking merges.

{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_warning}}

The ClickHouse background merge pool on {{host.name}} is becoming saturated. Monitor for further increase.

{{/is_warning}}
